# Implement ContainerSupervisor (DynamicSupervisor)

Create a DynamicSupervisor to manage ContainerManager processes.

## Requirements

- DynamicSupervisor for container processes
- Named registry for lookup
- Graceful shutdown handling
- Health check integration

## Acceptance Criteria

- [ ] `lib/pag_server/containers/container_supervisor.ex` exists
- [ ] Uses `DynamicSupervisor` behavior
- [ ] `start_container/1` starts a ContainerManager under supervisor
- [ ] `stop_container/1` gracefully stops container process
- [ ] `which_containers/0` lists active container pids
- [ ] Added to application supervision tree
- [ ] Unit tests for start/stop operations
